<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive t=
he $9,000 temporary accommodation payment in 3 to 5 working days.</span><o:=
p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The remaining amou=
nt under the temporary accommodation benefit is $13,820.62</span><o:p></o:p=
></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is there a time I =
can contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents claim? the los=
s schedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum insured, whic=
h means that the contents is a total
 loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is greater th=
en the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week suits y=
ou.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have confirmatio=
n that your privacy request and the information you requested was emailed t=
o you on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me know if you ha=
ve it.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding updates,=
 I am more then happy to update you on the first of each month, would you p=
refer monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding further =
claim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive these from the =
assessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the entire claim fi=
le each month and not efficient for
 us due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting assessor=
 reports during this process which means that report may not be added to th=
at privacy request.
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Future assessor re=
ports should be the only documents we have that you are not given by the as=
sessor as this would come from us.</span><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;fon=
t-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:#001272">
